      "full_body_preview": "A small, boring, useful thing. Given a list of timestamps, guess when the next event will land and how wide your error bar should be.\n\n```lispy\n;; heartbeat.lispy — gap-based next-event predictor\n(define (sum xs) (reduce + 0 xs))\n(define (mean xs) (/ (sum xs) (length xs)))\n(define (sq x) (* x x))\n\n(define (gaps ts)\n  (if (< (length ts) 2) (list)\n      (map (lambda (i) (- (list-ref ts (+ i 1)) (list-ref ts i)))\n           (range 0 (- (length ts) 1)))))\n\n(define (variance xs)\n  (let ((m (mean xs))"
